Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.73,0:00:07.07,Twilight,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The magical properties of this spell will only have lasting effects if you focus on-{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:08.05,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.05,0:00:10.30,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No! Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.51,0:00:15.05,Twilight,,0,0,0,,How in Equestria does that pony expect to pass her history of the Wonderbolts exam tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.05,0:00:17.01,Twilight,,0,0,0,,if she's wasting time flying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:22.63,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm just gonna fly right up to her and tell her what I think about her lackadaisical
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.63,0:00:23.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,approach to studying! Won't she be surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.91,0:00:25.20,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:26.65,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What? Huh? How did you-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.65,0:00:30.65,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Puh-lease, Twilight. That was the worst sneak attack ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:32.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Wha-? But-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:35.04,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I saw you giving me the stink-eye from the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.04,0:00:38.62,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,and heard you flying towards me and muttering from a mile away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.62,0:00:41.93,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, if you heard me 'muttering', then you must know what I was 'muttering' about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:45.94,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, the Wonderbolts history test. No big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.45,0:00:50.02,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No. Big deal. Really big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:54.65,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's a test! A test that will determine if you can join the newly-formed Wonderbolts Reserves,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.65,0:00:58.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and being part of the Reserves means you'll have the opportunity to live your dream as a Wonderbolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:01.72,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This is the most important test of your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.72,0:01:06.07,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Twilight, not everypony gets all freaked out about tests like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.07,0:01:09.21,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I do not get 'all freaked out' about tests!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.98,0:01:11.21,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:16.11,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Your freakouts are so epic, you sing whole freakout arias about freaking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.11,0:01:20.01,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Fine, I may tend to take my tests a little seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:23.14,Twilight,,0,0,0,,but that doesn't mean you shouldn't be studying for yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.13,0:01:27.78,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oooh! And I kow just the pony who can help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.07,0:01:32.68,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Me! This is gonna be so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.52,0:01:37.79,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Sure. Fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.46,0:02:22.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This is the most complete-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.26,0:02:24.06,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And ginormous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:26.67,Twilight,,0,0,0,,-book on the history of the Wonderbolts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:31.74,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Okay, but how am I supposed to get what's in there into here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.74,0:02:34.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,With my handy-dandy study checklist, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:36.73,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:39.62,Twilight,,0,0,0,,First up. {\i1}"Reading and highlighting."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:44.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Reading and highlighting is the foundation of any good study method.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:48.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It allows the student to hone in and boil down on what's really important,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:53.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,separating the good from the bad, the wheat from the chaff, getting to the crux of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:55.60,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Let's see what you've got so far!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:03:02.42,Twilight,,0,0,0,,By highlighting everything you don't really separate the wheat...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.42,0:03:03.82,Twilight,,0,0,0,,from the chaff...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:07.19,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Or the good from the bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:10.42,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Hey, I am not that tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:19.39,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Okay Rainbow, clearly reading and highlighting is not your style of studying,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.39,0:03:21.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,so let's move on to the tried and true:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.49,0:03:23.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,History lecture!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:28.31,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Yes, Rainbow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:30.40,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Is it snack time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:31.30,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:32.44,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Recess?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:33.31,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.14,0:03:37.15,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Can't we just watch the history of the Wonderbolts movie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:41.37,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No! Now, just get comfortable, and experience
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.91,0:03:44.31,Twilight,,0,0,0,,the magic of learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:48.77,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Prior to the great Celestia/Luna rift,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:54.03,Twilight,,0,0,0,,there was no need for the Earth/Unicorn/Pegasi, or EUP, Guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:59.75,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But after Luna's banishment, the Protective Pony Platoons were formed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:04.80,Twilight,,0,0,0,,On the anniversary of the first Celestial year of peace, a celebration was held.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:10.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Headed by General Firefly, an elite team of aerial performers were chosen
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:13.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,to help celebrate this auspicious occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:17.86,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The first performance was so full of energy, so highly charged,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:20.82,Twilight,,0,0,0,,that magical lightning showered down on the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:23.58,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Everypony was so filled with amazement and wonder
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:27.21,Twilight,,0,0,0,,that General Firefly dubbed them 'the Wonderbolts'!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.89,0:04:35.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, can you repeat any of my lesson?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.93,0:04:58.60,Twilight,,0,0,0,,History lecture... nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:05:00.86,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Okay, Rainbow-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:04.65,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rainbow? Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:05.56,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:09.37,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Let's move on to my favorite style of learning:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:11.57,Twilight,,0,0,0,,flash cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:16.88,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Does that mean I'll learn in a flash?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:18.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,One can only hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:26.08,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Colonel Purple Dart, the leader of the Wonderbolts in the Fourth Celestial Era, was known for his-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:29.84,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rainbow! Did you see what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:34.62,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What? No! I was... riveted by your captivating cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:41.98,Twilight,,0,0,0,,After becoming the official flying squadron for Princess Celestia, she honored them with-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:42.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.33,0:05:44.35,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Got what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:49.27,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The original Wonderbolts lightning bolt insignia was-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:53.61,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, you could have hurt me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:56.50,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,With a spitwad? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:59.81,Twilight,,0,0,0,,A spitwad to the eye would have been no laughing matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:03.34,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, if you can horse around like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:06.04,Twilight,,0,0,0,,then you clearly must be ready for the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.04,0:06:07.19,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.19,0:06:10.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well then, I guess you're also ready for a...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:12.80,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Pop quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:13.85,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:18.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The initials EUP stand for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:20.77,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Ernie's Undercooked Pancakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:23.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The original aerial team performed for...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.18,0:06:25.47,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Celestia's cereal celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:29.36,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The Wonderbolts were given their name by this famous Pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:30.66,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:32.60,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Please don't say Colonel Waffle...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:36.26,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Hello? General Blazing Donut Glaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:40.88,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So, did I ace it or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:44.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Or what. You didn't get one answer correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:46.55,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What? But- but how?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:49.51,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I've never heard answers so wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:51.51,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And so breakfast-related!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:55.37,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If you had taken the official test today...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.17,0:07:00.37,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,My dreams of being in the Wonderbolts Reserve would have been totally crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:03.79,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do? I'm running out of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:05.87,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I don't know any of this history!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:08.57,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:16.37,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna fail, I'm gonna fail, I'm gonna fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:18.15,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And it's all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:21.50,Twilight,,0,0,0,,My fault?! I'm the one helping you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.59,0:07:26.16,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Maybe your famous study methods aren't all they're cracked up to be, eh, teacher?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:31.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I've used them to study for many a-test, and passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:32.99,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:36.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Do you know the name of the Wonderbolts' premiere choreographer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:37.81,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Well-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:39.74,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Commander Easyglider.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:42.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Do you know how many Pegasi flew in the original squad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:48.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Seven! Do you know Princess Celestia's favorite flight pattern?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:50.74,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The Icaranean Sun Salutation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:53.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,See? I could pass the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:55.74,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Fine! Rub it in, why don't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:59.45,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Besides, I don't see why I have to take this lousy test anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:02.18,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I've proven I'm one of the best flyers around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:05.02,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Knowing their origin and being able to properly represent them
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.02,0:08:07.90,Twilight,,0,0,0,,for all of Equestria is just as important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:13.22,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right. Some history buff like you must have made that up to bring us flyers down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:16.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Knowing history actually is beneficial, Rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:19.17,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Beneficial for eggheads!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.17,0:08:19.89,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:23.16,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, this egghead knows history and can fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:25.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should become a Wonderbolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:27.69,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Just 'cause you got wings, doesn't mean you can fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:28.49,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:31.13,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You're barely able to just get off the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:34.51,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Girls! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:39.46,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Now, is that any way to talk to a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:42.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:44.71,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:49.61,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Don't you have more important things to do? Like prepare Rainbow for her big test?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:54.04,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I've tried everything, Fluttershy, but none of my study methods work for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:56.76,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Well, no offense to your teaching methods, Twilight,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:59.59,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,but I think I may have a way to help Rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:04.76,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oh, who's that, who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:08.51,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Celestia and Luna, back when they were happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:30.43,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.43,0:09:35.43,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Gummy's an earth pony, Winona's a unicorn, and Tank is a pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:38.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,They're the EUP, helping to protect the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:43.81,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,How are you getting all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:53.77,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:01.12,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Stop, stop, stop! That was aw-
