Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:05.02,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I give a three whoo-hoos. Whoo-hoo! Whoo-hoo! Whoo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:07.83,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And an extra whoo for good measure. Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:11.17,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Well I give it a whoa-whoa-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:15.28,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'm totally confused and I just wanna go home.
