Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:22.89,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Some ponies learn through theatrical presentation, but other ponies learn through musical intervention.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.11,0:10:32.78,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Well, back in ancient times, there were the Wonderbolts of old \N{\alpha&HFF&} просто выравниваю всю песню по высоте
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:34.84,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,A general named Firefly, amazing and so...\N{\alpha&HFF&}Bold!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:35.44,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,A general named Firefly, amazing and so...\N{\rSomepony}Bold!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:37.36,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,She brought them all together, spreading unity... \N{\alpha&HFF&} In flight
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:37.96,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,She brought them all together, spreading unity... \N{\rSomepony}In flight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:39.72,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Performing at their very best with wonder...\N{\alpha&HFF&} and we mighn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:40.52,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Performing at their very best with wonder...\N{\rSomepony}And with might!
