Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:44.99,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Gave Wonderbolts a bit of steel along with\N{\alpha&HFF&} lots of heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:45.87,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Gave Wonderbolts a bit of steel along with\N{\rSomepony} Lots of heart!
