Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.74,0:10:48.22,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,An admiral named Fairy Flight and general called \N{\rSomepony}Flash
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.22,0:10:49.88,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Helped the 'bolts fly super high\N{\alpha&HFF&} With style and panache!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:51.04,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Helped the 'bolts fly super high\N{\rSomepony} With style and panache!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:53.00,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Commander Easy Glider was the real cream of… \N{\alpha&HFF&}The crop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:53.64,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Commander Easy Glider was the real cream of… \N{\rSomepony}The crop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:55.07,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,For with their wicked moves, the Wonderbolts  \N{\alpha&HFF&} soared to the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:56.25,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,For with their wicked moves, the Wonderbolts \N{\rSomepony}soared to the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:58.33,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Wonderbolts, yeah! Wonderbolts… \N{\alpha&HFF&} Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.33,0:10:59.02,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Wonderbolts, yeah! Wonderbolts… \N{\rSomepony} Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:00.97,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Wonderbolts, yeah! Wonderbolts… \N{\alpha&HFF&} Uuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:01.48,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Wonderbolts, yeah! Wonderbolts… \N{\rSomepony} Uuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.48,0:11:04.52,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,That is my rappin' Hist'ry of the Wonderbolts!  \N{\alpha&HFF&} просто выравниваю всю песню по высоте
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:07.32,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,So, did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:08.56,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yes, Pinkie Pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.06,0:11:15.84,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,General This and Colonel That, they're Wonderbolts, something that rhymes with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:19.11,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,That… was pretty terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:22.41,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What? No. Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:25.13,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But I've gotta learn this stuff. Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:28.64,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And I am just the pony to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:31.88,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Rarity, you look ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:35.45,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'm going to ignore that comment out of my desire to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.49,0:11:37.52,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:41.10,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Get ready, Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:46.10,Rarity,,0,0,0,,For I am going to take you on an historical adventure in fashion!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.91,0:11:54.70,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I am now modelling the rather unattractive and frankly itchy original Wonderbolts flying costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:12:03.24,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, thanks to the vision of Flair-du-Mare the Wonderbolts ensemble became more streamlined and wonderfully breathable fabric.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:06.97,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Of course, there were fashion hits and misses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:13.21,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Just look at those dreadful bellbottoms. What were ponies thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:16.63,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I bet general Flash wrapped these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:18.60,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Pinkie, you're real!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:19.67,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Of course I'm real.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:25.18,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I mean I'm not the real general Flash the tenth leader of the Wonderbolts. But I, Pinkie, am really real.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:29.08,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,And I'm Admiral Fairy Flight from the seventh squadron.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:32.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And of course you recognize Commander Easy Glider.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:36.70,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And I'm sporting some sort of getup worn by Colonel Purple Dart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:39.34,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Just look at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.34,0:12:40.65,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Look at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:42.11,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:44.19,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,It's too much for my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.19,0:12:46.30,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Now, don't you fret, Rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:49.48,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,This fashion show nonsence wouldn't help me learn nothing either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.05,0:12:51.87,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:55.17,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Well, what special study trick do you have, AJ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:57.71,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Who, me? Oh, I got nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.18,0:13:02.71,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I can tell you every little thing there's to know about the history of apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:06.86,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,But I picked that up over years in the field as a labour of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.86,0:13:08.48,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,How much time you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:09.68,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Twelve hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:12.48,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Oh, then you are up a creek.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:18.30,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, I think we should just go back to old-fashioned studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:20.24,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,What about our play?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:27.10,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Just look at these costumes. Surely something resonates with your inner Wonderbolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:30.27,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And Granny Smith discovered the first granny smith in Fillydelphia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.27,0:13:31.71,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,When she was just a filly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:34.37,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Commander Easyglider was the real cream of the crop…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:37.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Pinkie, stop rapping. That isn't gonna help Rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:40.30,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Well, I suggest you put down your silly cards of flash
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.30,0:13:43.09,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,For I know that they cannot help our good friend Raindbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:49.72,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:50.60,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,No rapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:51.36,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,No cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:52.06,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,No costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:53.85,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,No play.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:56.04,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And no apples!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:59.13,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I am never gonna pass this test! Ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:00.78,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Just forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:17.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rainbow, I'm sorry about all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:19.71,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We didn't mean to overwhelm you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:22.50,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,It's okay. You were just trying to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:25.86,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,It's just too bad I'm too dumb to learn anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:27.47,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You are not dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:29.50,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You just learn differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:33.76,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,If by "differently" you mean "not at all", than you're totally right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:36.39,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No, that's totally wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:38.40,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,See, wrong again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:43.68,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't know anypony that's read more Daring Doo books than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:46.53,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Well, that's not gonna get me into the Wonderbolts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:50.13,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And your knowledge of jokes and pranks is only rivalled by Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:51.17,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.17,0:14:56.25,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,My years of being a class clown prevented me from actually learning how to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:14:58.35,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:15:01.07,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You are smart, creative, inventive and…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:03.15,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:05.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I know you're upset, but you don't need to…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:10.20,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:12.08,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I almost slammed into that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.08,0:15:12.86,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.86,0:15:15.50,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You were jabbering on so much you didn't even notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.50,0:15:17.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But how did you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:19.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You were listening and talking to me the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:21.91,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You are such a rookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:25.02,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,An experienced flyer like me knows how to multitask.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:26.61,Twilight,,0,0,0,,While you fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:27.81,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I's essential
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.81,0:15:29.50,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was paying attention to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.50,0:15:32.87,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,but was also scanning the sky and the ground for any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:34.16,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:36.29,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Flying's not just flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:38.23,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,In order to stay safe in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:41.88,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I gotta hear and see everything down to the littlest detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:42.70,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,For instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.70,0:15:46.38,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I saw Applebloom, Sweetie Bell and Scootaloo come out of Sugarcube Corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:49.67,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,and from the looks of it, they had carrot cupcakes with sprinkles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:54.24,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And I'm thinking Big Mac sold a huge order of apples to Filthy Rich,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.24,0:15:56.50,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,cause I heard him give a very hearty...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.50,0:15:57.43,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.48,0:16:01.93,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I always make note of everything when I fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:02.82,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,No biggie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.01,0:16:05.16,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.16,0:16:05.86,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:06.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:09.49,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:12.95,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want to hang out with a loser like me either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.76,0:16:24.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Thanks for meeting me, everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:25.75,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What is it, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:28.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We have to help Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:30.47,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Yes, but how?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.66,0:16:32.88,Rarity,,0,0,0,,We've tried every kind of studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:34.83,Rarity,,0,0,0,,My way, your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:37.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But we haven't tried Rainbow Dash's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:39.98,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I'm intrigued.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:41.82,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.82,0:16:42.86,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Listen up, ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:44.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Here's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.66,0:16:50.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Hey Rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:52.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Wanna go for a fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:54.46,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:56.13,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Got nothing better to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.40,0:17:01.36,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Didn't we just do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:02.80,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Yes, but like you said,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:05.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm such a newbie I need all the practice I can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:11.13,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, I'm sure you'll become a great flyer in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:13.93,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,After all, you're good at everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:18.62,Twilight,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:20.03,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:21.22,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:23.60,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Just getting my dreams crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.58,0:17:26.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Read any good books lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:29.12,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Just history books.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.12,0:17:30.50,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'd tell you what they're about
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:33.19,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,but my brain is as dry as a rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:35.98,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Speaking of rocks...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.98,0:17:39.62,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Did you know Pinkie Pie grew up on a rock farm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:42.73,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll go work there since I have no other plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:44.53,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,For the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:46.08,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on now, Rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:48.04,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You can't give up on your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:50.92,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Seems my dream is giving up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:52.88,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll learn to shine shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:54.10,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Sell hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:17:55.46,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Dig ditches.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:17:57.88,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Or maybe you'll be a Wonderbolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:17:59.87,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Twilight, give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:01.52,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:08.30,Twilight,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:10.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,what do you remember about that flight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:12.56,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:15.63,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Except after Luna was banished to the moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:17.69,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Celestia needed protective forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.69,0:18:20.83,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So Earth, Unicorn and Pegasi formed the EUP guard
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:23.13,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,of the protective pony platoons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:25.32,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.71,0:18:26.75,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:29.83,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,at the celebration of the first Celestial Year of Peace
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:31.85,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,an elite flying squadron performed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:36.10,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,headed by General Fiery Flight, who later named the group "The Wonderbolts".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.10,0:18:37.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.10,0:18:39.80,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Commander Easy Glider established flight choreography
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:42.47,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,that is still used by the Wonderbolts today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:43.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:46.10,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I... I know the history!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:47.56,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I know it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:50.57,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But how in Equestria did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:52.02,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You learned it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:53.76,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I got that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.76,0:18:54.94,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:56.51,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, on our first flight
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:19:00.20,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I discovered that you catalog everything that happens all around you when you're flying
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:02.13,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Without even thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:04.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:07.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I made use of your special skills by enlisting everypony
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:10.22,Twilight,,0,0,0,,to help you learn the history of the Wonderbolts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.70,0:19:13.77,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I, Princess Celestia,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.77,0:19:16.68,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,banish you, Princess Luna, to the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.68,0:19:19.11,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Nooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:24.39,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:25.80,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Unicorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.80,0:19:27.50,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:28.56,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,E!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:29.64,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,U!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:31.07,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,P!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:31.89,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.24,0:19:35.99,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Let us celebrate our first Celestial year of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:37.42,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's party!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:38.90,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I'm general Firefly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:41.44,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Gee, my costume is itchy and unattractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.44,0:19:44.04,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,But I'm going to assemble an awesome flying team!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:46.36,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I'll call them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.36,0:19:48.87,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,The Wonderbolts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:51.46,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Streamlined style by Flair-du-Mare.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:53.38,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Admiral Fairweather.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:55.50,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Colonel Purple Dart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:58.55,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Admiral Fairy Flight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:00.12,Somepony,,0,0,0,,General Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.12,0:20:02.47,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Commander Easyglider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.14,0:20:19.40,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,The history of the Wonderbolts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.23,0:20:22.53,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh, oh my gosh, oh my gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:23.56,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.56,0:20:25.87,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Thank you all so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:26.90,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:28.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But it all came from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.38,0:20:31.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You learned without knowing you're learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:33.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Your main focus is flying,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:36.37,Twilight,,0,0,0,,but then your brain is also absorbing lots of other information.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.37,0:20:38.82,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's actually really brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:42.24,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I always knew I was brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.32,0:20:48.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash finally learned the history of the Wonderbolts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.40,0:20:51.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But she is not the only pony that needed a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:54.13,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I needed to learn something just as important.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:56.78,Twilight,,0,0,0,,One way of learning isn't better than another.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:21:00.84,Twilight,,0,0,0,,After all, everypony is unique and individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:33.74,Rarity,,0,0,0,,SCHASTLIVY PONETC
